Params: {2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'The abandoned dock the liaison mentioned is up ahead.', 4: '1'}

{2: 'Lee', 3: "I can't help but feel like we're walking into a trap. Regardless of our first encounter or during dinner last night, he had a strange look about him whenever this place is mentioned.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: "I'm sure we'll know when we get there. So, let's keep moving.", 4: '1'}
{2: '???', 3: '...The leader of the ARU and members of Babylonia, eh?'}
{2: '???', 3: "If you move an inch, we've got bullets with your names on it."}
{3: 'The man glares at you before turning to operate the radio station.'}
{2: '???', 3: "...Got it. If you think it's okay, then no problem."}
{3: 'The man puts down the receiver and turns to face you and the others.'}
{2: '???', 3: 'You may pass, Mr. Staessen. Mr. Antonov says hello to you.'}
{2: '???', 3: "He's in the ruins of the office building up ahead. Sergey is also waiting for you... all."}
{2: 'Staessen', 3: "Someone I know... But he's on the same as Sergey now?", 4: '1'}
